WEBVTT

00:00:07.921 --> 00:00:10.361
Baada ya vita ya nuklea vya kusikitisha

00:00:10.361 --> 00:00:14.661
Lilith Iyapo anaamka baada ya
miaka 250 ya mapumziko

00:00:14.661 --> 00:00:18.857
kujikuta amezungukwa na kundi la
viumbe linaloitwa Oankali.

00:00:18.857 --> 00:00:21.737
Hawa viumbe walioendelea sana
walitaka kubadilishana DNA

00:00:21.737 --> 00:00:23.157
kwa kuzaliana na binadamu

00:00:23.157 --> 00:00:27.517
ili kila kinasaba cha kiumbe kisambae
na kiwe na nguvu kushinda kingine.

00:00:27.517 --> 00:00:32.257
Njia pekee wanayotoa ni kinga ya uzazi
kwa jamii yote ya binadamu.